    Contains options that specify what travel time information to retrieve.

    Travel times are returned for a specific time and then for subsequent times with a specified time interval. For example, if neither departure nor arrival time is specified, but there is an interval of 15 minutes and 4 travel times requested, then the travel time for the current time will be returned, as well as travel times for 15 minutes from now, 30 minutes from now, and 45 minutes from now.

    Departure time and arrival time are optional parameters. If neither is specified, then the current time is used.
